item.title: Matinee Monday: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles II: The Secret of the Ooze LIVE! (w/ Adam Pally)
item.description: Go Ninja! Go Ninja! Go!!! Adam Pally joins Paul, Jason, and June to discuss Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles II: The Secret of the Ooze LIVE from Irving Plaza in New York City. They cover the horrific amount of pizza, why these are the most charmless turtles imaginable, April O’Neil’s strange relationship with the turtles, and more. Plus, we hear from Vanilla Ice himself on how Ninja Rap was born. (Originally released 06/26/2015) HDTGM is going on tour this August! Tix on sale at hdtgm... Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/Ao0C24M8
